data.description: Your search is over! Here is an amazing home in the gated community of The Summit nestled in the  foothills of Northeast Bakersfield. This 3 bedroom/2.5 bath, 2,493 sqft, split-wing home offers a large formal living room, dining room and family room with high vaulted ceilings as well as a 3 car garage. A spacious open kitchen with granite countertops and modern appliances will awaken the chef in you. Entertain your guests in the spacious, beautifully landscaped back yard with covered patio. This home is equipped with solar panels to help with those high bills. Easy access to SR178  freeway, shopping, and eateries. One mile from Highland High and 3.7 miles from Bakersfield  College.
